   578→As a convenience, helper constants are exported to provide information about what `node-semver` supports:
   579→
   580→### `RELEASE_TYPES`
   582→- major
   583→- premajor
   584→- minor
   585→- preminor
   586→- patch
   587→- prepatch
   588→- prerelease
